metadata.name: London
metadata.description:
London, 2018

From a series of photos taken on a short trip to Great Britain back in 2018

Shot with an early version of the Voigtländer Bessa R2 and a Jupiter 8 lens

On Kodak Portra 400, 35mm negative film

This photo was taken on a little trip I took with my sister back in 2018, and it is one of my first encounters with film photography. I received the prints a couple of weeks later and fell in love with the density of memories packed into each one; since then, film as a medium has changed my perception of photography and highly influenced my way of telling stories. 

1/1 NFT
4155 x 6428 pixels
